		"description": "<p>At 15th level, if you can get to them in time, there&rsquo;s virtually nobody you can&rsquo;t save. You learn the @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.omvngnmoo75is54f]{Spare the Dying} cantrip.</p>\n<p>Additionally, once per long rest, you may cast @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.0k5zymq9q95l8jwa]{Revivify} without material components. If you have already used this feature, you may use it again a number of times equal to half your proficiency bonus, but you require one use of a healer&rsquo;s kit to do so (it is consumed in the process).</p>",
